instruction: Name as many types of artificial intelligence as you can.
output:
Types of artificial intelligence include: 
- Machine learning 
- Natural language processing 
- Computer vision 
- Robotics 
- Expert systems 
- Neural networks 
- Genetic algorithms 
- Fuzzy logic
- Virtual agents 
- Autonomous agents 
- Predictive analytics 
- Data mining 
- Reinforcement learning 
- Deep learning.
